vec3-class.description:
A very useful and powerful tool for calculating vector operations, this is a class that simplifies everything. Here are basic examples ```js
const vec = Vec3(0,0,0);
const vec = new Vec3(0,0,0);
const vec = Vec3.from({x:0,y:0,z:0});
const vec = Vec3.from([0,0,0]);```
Chaining Example ```js
const vec = Vec3.form(player.location)
.add(Vec3(0,5,0))
.multiply(3)
.add({x:0,y:-5,z:0});
```
